All,

Please review the updated remote work policy taking effect October 1, 2025.

Key changes:
1. All remote work requires a VPN connection via WireGuard (replacing the old OpenVPN setup)
2. Company laptops must have full-disk encryption enabled
3. Personal devices are no longer permitted for accessing production systems
4. Two-factor authentication is mandatory for all services, no exceptions

WireGuard configuration guides will be distributed next week. If you haven't installed the WireGuard client yet, please do so before October 1.

Questions? Let me know.

Daniel Okafor
Head of IT

