Team,

The Q3 security audit from CypherGuard is complete. Summary:

- 3 critical vulnerabilities identified
- 7 medium-severity issues
- 12 low-severity/informational findings

Critical items:
1. SQL injection in the legacy reporting endpoint (/api/v1/reports/custom)
2. Insecure session handling in the admin dashboard
3. Missing rate limiting on the authentication API

All 3 critical vulnerabilities have been patched as of October 8, 2025. Medium-severity items are scheduled for the October sprint.

Full report attached (see CypherGuard portal for details).

Omar

